There are three classes of tournaments:
    \n\nA: Experienced Players Only—red Kiosks;
    rules are not taught before or during play;
    \n\nB: Beginners Allowed—yellow kiosks;
    game will be taught ONLY at the listed Demo
    time. For subsequent rounds, the Class is A;
    \n\nC: Coached—green kiosks; game will
    be taught during or just prior to event start
    in event location. Once past the Preliminary
    round, the Class is always A.
